#### Option 1: Scenario A -- HD Supply (Tier 2, different customer)

**Setup**: Use a clean browser profile or InPrivate, then log into portal as Derek.

1. Open portal: https://zurnelkaycustomercare.powerappsportals.com
2. Login using `derek.lawson` / `ZeDemo!2026`
3. Click chat widget (bottom-right bubble)
4. Bot greets customer
5. **As Derek**: "My E-Z Flush sensor isn't detecting users. We have 8 units at a hotel and they're all acting up."
6. If prompted in chat, click **Login** and complete sign-in (same Derek credentials)
7. Bot surfaces KB/troubleshooting content for AquaVantage / E-Z Flush
8. **As Derek**: "I've already tried batteries, sensor cleaning, and water pressure checks. Can I talk to someone?"
9. Bot escalates to live agent
10. **Switch to CS Workspace** -- accept incoming chat
11. Show: HD Supply account, Tier 2 orange badge, Derek Lawson contact, bot transcript
