8. Open case -- show timeline (Rachel email, quality batch review, warranty note)
9. Agent sees: defect confirmed, 200 units to 3 distributors, Tier 1 = 48-hour RMA
10. **Cross-reference**: Rachel asks about PO #94820 filters -- confirm batch WS-2026-0303 is verified-good
11. Resolution: Issue RMA, ship replacements, proactive recall to Hajoca + Pacific Plumbing

**Key demo point**: Same account as phone scenario but different channel, different contact, different issue. Full customer 360 carries across all interactions. Tier 1 gets priority RMA turnaround.

